creator: Winkl
descriptionHtml:
Winkl helps you get brand collaborations from top brands in India such as Flipkart, Amazon etc.

Winkl is a community of Content Creators & Influencers - For Instagrammers, Youtubers, Tiktok stars, artists, photographers, bloggers alike to come together, view each other’s work, learn about content creation and collaborate with top brands.

Collaborate with top brands
On the Winkl app, you can access curated brand collaborations from top brands in India. The collaborations section as all the right tools which help you manage your brand collaborations easily without any hassle. Right from applying to campaigns, getting shortlisted, payments (barter + paid), accessing the content brief, generating invoices and tracking payments.

Learn the secrets to content creation
Learn and share how great content gets created. Go behind the scenes with content creators, bloggers and influencers and learn how they pose, create flatlays, pose for fashion photoshoots, create beauty looks and so much more. On Winkl, you just don’t see the content, you learn how it was created.

Create your own digital media kit
You can now create your digital media kit and share it with brands and PR agencies by just sharing your Winkl profile link!This will help you showcase your work easily and get more brand collaborations.

What is a media kit?
A media kit is a document that outlines the key facts and statistics about your blog, Youtube channel or other social accounts. Generally, a media kit is shared with potential advertisers or brands that you want to collaborate with. It lets marketers know all about your content, your niche, and your audience count. A media kit can also list collaboration options and prices for the services you offer. A thorough, ready to send Media Kit is a must for professional collaborations with brands and potential advertisers.

Your media kit will include the follower count on your blog, Instagram and other social platforms, your engagement ratio, your previous collaborations with other brands, your best work, other achievements and your payment preferences for collaborations (paid/barter).


Showcase your best work
Get verified and showcase your best work by sharing your content’s journey from ideation to creation. This gives other influencers and brands some little insight into all the hard work and challenges you as a content creator faced in the process.

This enables you to get direct feedback from other great content creators and also inspire and mentor many upcoming content creators in your niche. Talking about your best work and sharing it with brands, PR agencies and other content creators will give them an idea of your skills and what potential campaigns will look like if they collaborate with you.

Get inspired by learning how great content gets created
On Winkl, some great verified content creators share their secrets on how they create content that their audience likes and is appreciated by brands for collaborations. If you are an aspiring blogger, influencer, youtube or any type of content creators, Winkl is the place to learn from the best in the industry. You can also directly engage with the community and get feedback and advice from well-established creators on how to get started on your own content creation journey, You can find mentors to guide you, experts to answer your queries and their work to inspire you.

If you are an established content creator who is passionate about creating content, Winkl is a great place for you to find like-minded creators to connect, interact and collaborate with and relevant brands to work with. In short, find a new family to work and engage with.

Download Winkl now and jump on board with us on a journey of collaborating with top brands and learning from the community
